    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Colposcelis jachontovi, habitus, details of structure and labels.A = Holotype, ♂, habitus dorsally; B = Holotype of C. kerzhneri, ♂, dorsally; C = paratype of C. kerzhneri, ♀, dorsally; D = labels of the holotype of C. jachontovi; E = labels of the holotype of C. kerzhneri; F = thorax and abdominal ventrite 1, female, ventrally." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10203166/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10203168>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Colposcelis jachontovi, details of structure. A = head dorsally; B = apical antennomeres, female; C = tegmen of aedeagus; D = median lobe of aedeagus; E = male inner sternite and tergite VIII; F = spiculum gastrale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10203168/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

